Description:
1. Login with standard_user credentials.
2. Click “Add to cart” on any two products.
3. Click the Cart icon.
4. Verify that both items are listed in the cart.
5. Click Remove on one item.
6. Verify that only one item remains in the cart.

Description:
1. Login with valid credentials. 
2. Add one item to the cart. 
3. Go to the cart and click Checkout. 
4. Fill in the checkout information: 
• First Name: John 
• Last Name: Doe 
• Zip/Postal Code: 12345 
5. Click Continue, then Finish. 
6. Verify that the confirmation message appears: “Thank you for your order!”.

Suite/Test/Step Name: click(findTestObject("Object Repository/CompleteCheckout/Page_Swag Labs/h2_Thank you for your order"))
click(findTestObject("Object Repository/CompleteCheckout/Page_Swag Labs/div_Your order has been dispatched, and wil_39390f"))
message = getText(findTestObject("CompleteCheckout/Page_Swag Labs/h2_Thank you for your order"))
verifyMatch(message, "Thank you for your order!", true)

Description:
1. Login and add one item to the cart. 
2. Proceed to checkout. 
3. Leave First Name, Last Name, or Zip Code field empty. 
4. Click Continue. 
5. Verify that an appropriate error message appears.

Suite/Test/Step Name: click(findTestObject("Object Repository/CheckoutValidationError/Page_Swag Labs/h3_Error First Name is required"))
h3Error = getText(findTestObject("Object Repository/CheckoutValidationError/Page_Swag Labs/h3_Error First Name is required"))
click(findTestObject("Object Repository/CheckoutValidationError/Page_Swag Labs/div_Error First Name is required"))
divError = getText(findTestObject("Object Repository/CheckoutValidationError/Page_Swag Labs/h3_Error First Name is required"))
click(findTestObject("Object Repository/CheckoutValidationError/Page_Swag Labs/button_Error First Name is required_error-button"))
verifyMatch(h3Error, "Error: First Name is required", true)
verifyMatch(divError, "Error: First Name is required", true)
